{"tid":412752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ 名宿批評紅軍兩人：有他們就無法贏","createTime":"2017-09-25T02:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T06:34:25.000Z","uid":57237,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9fae8857055a1718cc93c29f22ca6cf8fdff7f","tid":412752,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"曼聯名宿里奧費迪南表示，利物浦後防線的洛夫雲和摩蘭奴都不夠好。<br />\n<br />\n　　「我覺得雲迪積克毫無疑問會改進利物浦的實力，他本來可以成為中堅核心，他和馬迪普會組成很好的中堅搭檔。」里奧費迪南對入球網說。<br />\n<br />\n　　「我覺得洛夫雲不夠好，他在很長一段時間內，犯了很多錯。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「摩蘭奴的防守也不夠好，看他助攻向前讓人高興，但是你想要他首先做好防守，在這方面他做得還不夠。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「所以，你的4後衛中有這兩球員，你就會失敗。」<br />\n<br />\n　　（來自 肆客足球）"},{"pid":"4a68a94caab45dca1341fa1a3633813b6608f28d","tid":412752,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1303e516ab00fd66edbfc10b3d39e09af9029c","tid":412752,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:59:33.000Z","msg":"死獌狗，猁狗內政關你9事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b435257ca4ee60e5b0198c3a5447f4261af2d67c","tid":412752,"uid":33770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死獌狗，猁狗內政關你9事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講波都唔撚比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4bf904d0e41ee3b44bb8d9c6e58b844b71144f","tid":412752,"uid":124499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"洛夫雲派少陣膠已經當幫到好大忙"},{"pid":"8b591238a72726b5d1374750641f69ae4c7d052e","tid":412752,"uid":19552,"like"